Subject Re Nazi memoribilia From Christopher C May In Michael Brininstool writes Swatikas were also common in American Indian markings painted walls Is it the Swastika that is bad Just want to back this up with a personal My grandparents have a Navajo rug made in the 's which they received in trade from the weaver while living in Flagstaff The decorative motif consists of large black swastikas one in each What's more the color scheme is black white and To the casual glance it would undoubtedly appear to be a Nazi relic of some Yet they owned it ten years before Hitler and the National Socialists came to As I recall they took it down in the 's and didn't feel quite right about putting it back up until the ' It still draws comments from those who don't know what it ccm Christopher May of of Medicine ' Do your part for Liberty Teach your children to hate Big Do you care about freedom Dreams may have inspired it and wishes promoted it but only war and weapons have made it Robert Ardrey Armaque in armatos sumere jura Ovid The wise man's understanding inclineth him toward his right hand but a fool's heart turneth him to the Ecclesiastes Christopher May of of Medicine ' Do your part for Liberty Teach your children to hate Big